            <p style="color: rgba(25,79,144,0.65); font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.75; margin: 1.5rem 0;">Michael founded Capital Wealth in 2009 with a mission: help families retire with clarity, confidence, and a plan that actually works. Over 650 clients and $500M+ in assets later, he's built a practice focused entirely on retirement income planning, tax optimization, and fiduciary advice.</p>
            <p style="color: rgba(25,79,144,0.65); font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.75; margin: 1.5rem 0;">He hosts <em>Retire Right Radio</em> (Utah's #1 retirement radio show), wrote <em>Retire Right, Retire Now</em>, and serves on the Junior Achievement of Utah board. No sales pitches. No product pushing. Just straight talk about retirement.</p>
